com.rockhoppertech.music.midi.js

Class MIDISender

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rockhoppertech.music.midi.js.MIDISender

  • public class MIDISender
extends Object
    Shoves data directly to a channel on a device. No real timing. Useful for GUI things like keyboards or sliders. 
    MIDINote note = MIDINoteBuilder.create()
                .channel(0)
                .startBeat(1d)
                .pitch(Pitch.D5)
                .duration(5d)
                .program(MIDIGMPatch.BANJO.getProgram())
                .build();

MIDISender sender = new MIDISender();
sender.play(note);
sender.closeDevice();
    Author:
    Gene De Lisa
